許し合える刹那 夜はきらめく
The moment we can forgive each other, the night sparkles.

1163
01:42:41,007 --> 01:42:44,907
雨、晴れ、カレイド
Rain, sun, kaleidoscope,

1164
01:42:44,907 --> 01:42:48,507
またとない空
a sky like no other.

1165
01:42:48,507 --> 01:42:53,307
相応しい旅路とは 君と歩くことさ
The appropriate journey is walking with you,

1166
01:42:53,307 --> 01:42:58,207
君と歩くことなんだ
it's walking with you.

1167
01:42:58,207 --> 01:43:01,807
「ただいま」を聞けば
When I hear "I'm home,"

1168
01:43:01,807 --> 01:43:06,607
「おかえり」って叫ぶよ
I'll shout "Welcome back!"

1169
01:43:06,607 --> 01:43:13,407
当たり前じゃないか
Isn't that obvious?

1170
01:43:13,407 --> 01:43:18,007
Parade, Parade, Parade! 輝くんだよ
Parade, Parade, Parade! It shines!

1171
01:43:18,007 --> 01:43:23,807
暗がりを満たすのは 君だ 僕だ
What fills the darkness is you, and me.

1172
01:43:23,807 --> 01:43:29,507
Parade, Parade, Parade! 輝くんだよ
Parade, Parade, Parade! It shines!

1173
01:43:29,507 --> 01:43:34,907
悔しさも 愛しさも 連れておいで
Bring along the regrets and the love.

1174
01:43:34,907 --> 01:43:38,707
風、夢、羽 飛び立てるさ
With the wind, dreams, and feathers, we can fly!

1175
01:43:38,707 --> 01:43:41,907
ささやかな祈りは 光
A small prayer is light,

1176
01:43:41,907 --> 01:43:45,507
終わりなき兆し
an endless omen.

1177
01:43:45,507 --> 01:43:49,007
君と 飛び込んでゆく
Diving in together with you,

1178
01:43:49,007 --> 01:43:50,207
素敵なスタートさ
it's a wonderful start.

1179
01:43:50,207 --> 01:43:55,007
ここから これから Our Bright
From here, from now, Our Bright...

1180
01:43:55,007 --> 01:43:57,307
Parade, Parade!

1181
01:43:57,307 --> 01:44:02,507
Our Bright Parade, Parade!

1182
01:48:29,862 --> 01:49:04,862
この後は もう1本グランプリ！
2026年もホロライブプロダクションをよろしくお願い致します！
Up next, another Grand Prix!
We look forward to your continued support of hololive production in 2026!

